01:12:13.162 --> 01:12:14.287
I don't think so.

01:12:14.497 --> 01:12:17.207
Hey, Jack, you know Vida Warren?

01:12:17.375 --> 01:12:20.585
No. I mean, uh, yeah.

01:12:20.795 --> 01:12:22.629
