to watch most of what I record.

01:23:17.075 --> 01:23:19.952
It's amazing what l've found
on these tapes.

01:24:11.296 --> 01:24:12.588
Good morning.

01:25:02.639 --> 01:25:03.973
Oh, God. Are you all right?

01:25:04.182 --> 01:25:05.391
- Carly.
